{"tid":1192100,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實班玩具撚周圍屌人多星 係咪弱撚智？","createTime":"2019-06-08T09:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T16:02:15.000Z","uid":87155,"like":52,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9e59eec3420f2463d089ee761808f4e98bae786f","tid":1192100,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:07:04.000Z","msg":"唔怪得比人屌玩具撚<br />\n話比總決賽 有星又屌 無星又笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得唔夠我地足波鬥<br />\n<br />\n成班玩具撚英雄主義上身 個個都要人1打幾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老鼠我都未聽過足波1人可以打哂11個位<br />\n<br />\n有球星都要屌 咁世界無強隊喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n黑哨無品就聽得多 因為人地多星個牌面勁就追住屌真係好撚弱智..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f34bd20b693c29a41c6d59e9c3fedf3d39acb5","tid":1192100,"uid":87155,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"真係on撚9 多星比人屌 真係玩具撚先會講得出<br />\n<br />\n足波最多都係屌人金錢足球 就係屌都屌一陣最後都係互屌黑哨之類 <br />\n但玩具撚就係追住人地隊勇士多球星 黎屌<br />\n但我睇番原來勇士 果5隻星 有3個 咩green之類 係自家青訓養出黎 都要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母吹到啤一聲 <br />\n養到勁都唔撚比<br />\n<br />\n之後隻中鋒係斷撚埋腳比人簽番黎 又當世界top5黎講 <br />\n得果個kd係好撚勁 25轉會 抵比人屌25 當奧雲轉去曼聯一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真<br />\n屌你老母你地果個玩具總決賽唔係世界最高水平既比賽黎？ 唔比人有球星既？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗到再講<br />\n<br />\n純粹覺得班玩具撚洗版屌隊波多星好撚弱智 <br />\n仲要隊球星波係比人炒左3場 又唔撚係屌黑哨打人金錢籃球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437b91fe2980386cd8e800315a47157f83e90691","tid":1192100,"uid":87155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"推撚到你班玩具撚黎博我"},{"pid":"8c424113cc583736639e2310716060232d32cb0b","tid":1192100,"uid":87155,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"437b91fe2980386cd8e800315a47157f83e90691","tid":1192100,"uid":87155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"推撚到你班玩具撚黎博我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:21:23.000Z","msg":"駁我"},{"pid":"5a23e9889256b178473d89a312818184744e6c7d","tid":1192100,"uid":243550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:27:17.000Z","msg":"完全駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed295cfbec2bb471a55aa3777317c08045212441","tid":1192100,"uid":171153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:29:43.000Z","msg":"呢句真"},{"pid":"30c0902c7c3f131ba94466c485b727387ee4984f","tid":1192100,"uid":129733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67f34bd20b693c29a41c6d59e9c3fedf3d39acb5","tid":1192100,"uid":87155,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"真係on撚9 多星比人屌 真係玩具撚先會講得出<br />\n<br />\n足波最多都係屌人金錢足球 就係屌都屌一陣最後都係互屌黑哨之類 <br />\n但玩具撚就係追住人地隊勇士多球星 黎屌<br />\n但我睇番原來勇士 果5隻星 有3個 咩green之類 係自家青訓養出黎 都要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母吹到啤一聲 <br />\n養到勁都唔撚比<br />\n<br />\n之後隻中鋒係斷撚埋腳比人簽番黎 又當世界top5黎講 <br />\n得果個kd係好撚勁 25轉會 抵比人屌25 當奧雲轉去曼聯一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal